Well, yes.
If only I knew!
And you, what's your relationship with alcohol?
Well, without being indiscreet, I don't want to put anyone at ease, but it does so much good to exchange these experiences.
We feel less alone.
Well, yes, it does good.
Me, alcohol, no thank you, it's water that I like.
No joke, I drank last night but it had been two weeks.
But it's true that I drink easily when there's some in front of me, but I'm not obliged to get completely drunk, just a few effects are enough.
but still, you need some glasses!
Okay.
We're in the same boat then, except I can't yet drink moderately when I drink!!
I'm super cool on a daily basis and I let loose when I've been drinking.
Yes, it's true, I analyzed it too.
People who love me hate me when I drink.
The others I made them mad and comfort me in stupidity.
Oh well, yes, it's moving, but it's not me!!
Besides, it's someone's birthday who is very important to me, I can't leave, I can't avoid it.
but clearly I don't lose sight of the fact that it's zero alcohol!!
Yep! And that will be a nice gift for you too.
I forget myself often.
It's true and it's a shame. Because it's for me that I have to do it, not easy to get it into my head.
It's something I've also understood over the years, it's that if it's not for us, we won't get there.
If it's for others, it's because we're not convinced we have a problem!!
