Hello everyone,
Here I am doing this post because since July 1st I've had a bad trip on LSD.
I have to say that before this bad trip I was shooting 20 pills a day and I was doing about 1 week every two months with heavy stuff (Taz, coke, LSD, and everything else)...For 3 years.
Now I am going to tell you how it passed.
Have a good week, I'm waiting for you.
We had planned with 3 colleagues to take 10 grams of speed, 1 gram of MDMA and 2 vials of LSD.
On Friday evening everyone is doing well
We consumed 5 grams of speed plus all the MD.
Saturday morning after a sleepless night I'm going to work just the morning from 9am to 12pm in the afternoon,
We did not continue.
I continued on my side to shoot cartridges and to type speed.
Late afternoon, evening arrives, 2 other colleagues join us and we had decided to take LSD on the beach (Personally, I wasn't reassured).
A colleague offered me a glass with a drop of the LSD vial.
I hesitated at first, then I told myself come on, I'll take it (something I shouldn't have).
The evening continues normally and the two other so-called colleagues had decided to make us really party hard, super colleagues....
On this famous beach there were people and one of the two colleagues said there's someone looking for trouble, we're going to fight...
I think the product should go down because I couldn't fight like that.
so I forced myself to resist the product
Paranoia is starting to engulf me, making a scene of everything.
The two other colleagues who hadn't taken anything, started looking for the guys who were mad at us.
I being totally infatuated, I thought it was going to end at any moment.
Time passes, nothing happens.
Briefly, we leave from the beach and then we go to my place.
I ask them if the guys are following us.
He does not answer.
We arrive at my place and he leaves me there all alone at my place with my girlfriend who was sleeping...
I continue my bad all night
Unable to sleep, I think and at the slightest noise I go out with a bat....
The day is rising and I am beginning to fall asleep because I had just realized that there was nothing.
Night passes normally.
I wake up and I am still under the effect of LSD and the rest
I told myself it's normal
So we were on Sunday and the next day I had to work.
The day is passing normally.
I type some bullets then I nap.
Sunday passes and Monday arrives
I still feel messy.
I still think it's normal with the box I bought....
So at 2 p.m. I had to take the job.
I eat a little and I take a big line of speed to have energy at work...
so I take the car and I go to work
Arrive at work, as soon as I open the store I start to feel dizzy, my heart starts beating at 200 and I feel like I'm going to faint.
By reassuring me, I'm going to buy some Snickers bars and something to drink.
After that I go back to work and another crisis...
Panicked, I called my mother... because my colleagues were not there....
After his mother brought me to the doctor
He asks me what I did and I empty my whole bag.
and my mother took it rather well in the end she knew I was shifty
